IRMO  Schulze  (1997)  60 Cal.App.4
th
  519 
[employer-provided auto and housing benefits were 
properly  considered  income  for  support  purposes]).  
Not  all  sources  of  free  housing  can  be  used  as  
income.  However,  such  benefits  may  be  considered  
for  deviation  from  guideline  under  
FC  §  4058. 
(
