th
 747). 
8. Self-Employment  Income 
Independent    contractors,    sole    proprietors,    “gig    
economy”   workers   and   business   owners   are   all   
terms    referring    to    self-employed    individuals.    
Methods for recording/reporting their incomes have 
evolved over the years and may include Schedule C 
or  corporate  tax  returns,  profit  and  loss  statements,  
