The  motion  must  be  accompanied  with  a  sworn  
affidavit  that  the  lack  of  notice  was  not  caused  by  
their avoidance of   service or inexcusable neglect and 
must be accompanied by a proposed pleading. (CCP 
§ 473.5(b)). 
