This misdemeanor includes the same elements as 
a 
CCP  §  1209.5  action.  Note  however,  that  the  
relevant  Jury  Instruction,  CALCRIM  No.  2700, 
provides  that  the  People  must  also  prove  that  
“The defendant had the ability to follow the Court 
Order” and that “The defendant willfully violated',
